<br />

<br />
And as far as LoY and GoD... have you not gotten your awsome LoY songs???  curing poison/disease/curses was worth the expansion by itself... let alone the useful zones.  GoD may be high end content, but again the average level 65 player can handle some of it and earn some awsome gear (EP level) for themselves WITHOUT flags.  Now just imagine if you are level 70, it will be cake to get this stuff.
<br />

<br />
People complaining about expantions to EQ irritates me to no end... I have even heard people say they wish it would just go back to basic eq and remove all expansions.  To quote someone else, if you want a game that doesn't change, go play Diablo.  (better yet, play Dungeon kepper 2 - its a better game than diablo <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-2.gif" border="0" alt="Big Smile" hspace="2" /> )  EQ changes, and that makes it better.  Without the expansions EQ would be dead and closed down already.  I dare anyone who &quot;hates&quot; an expansion to delete all the songs/spells/abilities they got from that expansion, as well as all armor/weapons, and sacrifice down to what ever the level cap was before it, stop using the teleporters and don;t even group with people that have stuff from the expansion, cause it sucks, right?
<br />

