				<td colspan="2"><span>I have one question bouncing around in my head about this expansion that I haven't seen anyone else ask.  Actually it's several questions in one...
<br />

<br />
How is the level cap change going to affect LDoN missions?  Right now a group of 65's can crusie thru a normal mission and get 51 points.  If these same guys are level 70 will they get mor points?  Will the mob levels increase?
<br />

<br />
If mob levels stay the same, we may see a group of six level 70 players finishing LDoNs in 10-15 minutes on average.  It will allow some classes to solo adventures easier.
<br />

<br />
On the other hand, it will open up more opportunities for some to try more (or any) hard LDoNs.
